column3: message:"We would like to share the great story of Ms. Frances! She was the recipient of the Pay it 4Ward award on KFOR-TV. She was nominated for this honor for her compassion and kindheartedness. She is
column5: very deserving of this award. Ms. Frances decided to use the award to improve her quality of life and purchase her first set of dentures at DDS Dentures + Implant Solutions of South OKC. It has been 7 years since she's had teeth of any kind! We are so honored and thankful she decided to let us serve her and join her in this wonderful moment of her life! We will be forever grateful for the day that we got to spend with the wonderful
column6:
Ms. Frances!

Click the link below to view her Pay it 4Ward story!

http://kfor.com/2017/06/28/i-love-my-customers-oklahoma-city-cashier-recognized-for-compassion-kind-heart/

Give us a call today to see how we can share a story like this with you! (405) 367-4427"
